<small> small text </small>

1. General: remove paragraph tags (<p>)
2. bold text: remove div elements, not h4, triple apostrophe
3. italic text: remove div elements, not h4, double apostrophe
4. sections/subsections/subsubsection: remove div elements, instead of diferrent heading types use the == notation
5. pre: remove class info
6. bullets and numbering: use * and # instead of ul/li, remove div elements and class
7. line one/line two: remove class info
8. math: remove class and id
9. centered text: use <center> instead of class
10. fontSize: use <big> and <small> instead of span class